Name: Morri Pot
Desc: Increases all teammates' ATK by 40%, lasting for 30m. Only effective for your own Resonator in Co-op Mode.
Bg: Beef hot pots made with mushroom soup base and other ingredients. The taste is delicious, retaining the original flavor of the dish. But the selection of materials and processing must be careful, and careful again. If hallucinations occur during consumption, please seek medical attention immediately.
